[
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_2",
    "text": "Ethical Questions",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.3075471677619717,
      0.045058139932641524,
      0.556603775688163,
      0.06696428591402147
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_0",
    "text": "· As You Read",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.08113207960870471,
      0.052325581631327944,
      0.23207546971744084,
      0.06696428559822558
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_1",
    "text": "Consider a conflict of interest you have encountered in your life. How did you resolve it?",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0886526123384329,
      0.07412790711542594,
      0.2509433974814615,
      0.14836148602343713
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_3",
    "text": "When you encounter an ethical decision and must choose a course of action, ask yourself these important questions:",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3075471615725595,
      0.0755813949939648,
      0.8433962234126705,
      0.10912698393562911
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_4",
    "text": "Is it against the law? Does it violate company or professional policies?",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3226415256082073,
      0.1177325589296219,
      0.864150934061604,
      0.1535773562678762
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_5",
    "text": "Even if everyone is doing it, how would I feel if someone did this to me?",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3226415134827287,
      0.154017856897997,
      0.8660377453851957,
      0.18750000011667928
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_6",
    "text": "Am I sacrificing long-term benefits for short-term gains?",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.32264150940417874,
      0.1918604657367925,
      0.8245282935517964,
      0.20932539678583661
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_7",
    "text": "The Ethical Decision-Making Process",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.30754718178924795,
      0.23255813994502497,
      0.7490565981029351,
      0.2514880954502144
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_8",
    "text": "Here are some steps to take if you find yourself in an ethical dilemma:",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.30754717134977216,
      0.2557043646148702,
      0.8396226358357173,
      0.2892441860386063
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_9",
    "text": "Identify the ethical dilemma.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3264150956847605,
      0.2993551585396042,
      0.598113211635994,
      0.31547619028563606
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_10",
    "text": "Discover alternative actions.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3264150956847605,
      0.31820436483773834,
      0.598113211635994,
      0.3343253965837702
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_11",
    "text": "Decide who might be affected.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3264151005911817,
      0.3372093020252147,
      0.6094339607295731,
      0.353197674646297
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_12",
    "text": "List the probable effects of the alternatives.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3264151138299738,
      0.3561046508805926,
      0.7169811223492712,
      0.3720930235016747
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_13",
    "text": "Select the best alternative.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.32641509623630016,
      0.37499999981691307,
      0.5716981162165299,
      0.3896329363248496
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_14",
    "text": "Using this process will enable you to make a more informed ethical choice. Making an ethical decision involves more people than just you.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3056603751127917,
      0.4010416668096825,
      0.8528301853347001,
      0.4534883716286389
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 15
  },
