  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_22",
    "text": "Mathematics A large company decided it would gives of its profits to charity. If the amount given was spread equally among five different charities, what frac- tion of the company's profits was given to each? What percent of the company's profits is this?",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
